    "en": {
      "title": "A stock of Chinese rice arrives",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "1000 MT of rice donated by China was handed over to Minister Bandula Gunawardena on behalf of the Ministry of Education.",
        "This is the first batch of 10,000 metric tons of rice supplied by China.",
        "The Chinese embassy says it hopes to provide this to children in 7,900 schools islandwide."
      ],
